ue pregamos\r\n</u><b>    C-C#            C       --------segura nota <i>C</i>\r\n</b><u>Porque erramos não sendo um?\r\n\r\n</u><u>  ( <i>G#</i>   <i>G</i>   <i>F</i> )\r\n</u><b>E|-----------------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>B|-----------------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>G|-5-5-5-5----6-6-6-----5-5-5-5----3-3-3---------|\r\n</b><b>D|-----------------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>A|-5-5-5-5----6-6-6-----5-5-5-5----3-3-3---------|  (2x)\r\n</b><b>E|-----------------------------------------------|\r\n\r\n</b><u>( <i>G#</i>   <i>G</i>   <i>F</i> )\r\n\r\n</u><b>E|-----------------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>B|-----------------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>G|-3-3-3-3---4-4-4------3-3-3-3----4-4-4---------|\r\n</b><b>D|-----------------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>A|-3-3-3-3---4-4-4------3-3-3-3----4-4-4---------|\r\n</b><b>E|-----------------------------------------------|\r\n\r\n</b><u>( <i>G</i>  <i>Bb</i>  <i>G</i>  <i>C</i> )\r\n\r\n</u><u>Solo de teclado: <i>Am</i>  <i>G#</i>\r\n\r\n</u><u>Intro de guitarra p/ solo:\r\n\r\n</u><b>E|--------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>B|--------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>G|--------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>D|--------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>A|-7---7-7----7-7--------6---6-6----6-7-|\r\n</b><b>E|--8-8-8-8--8-8-8--5-8---8-8-8-8--8-8--|\r\n\r\n</b><u>Solo de guitarra: <i>C</i>\r\n\r\n</u><u>Caiam os muros, tirem as pedras...\r\n</u><u>C|-<i>C#</i>               <i>C</i>-<i>Bb</i>\r\n</u><u>Ninguém pode se esconder de Deus</u>"
